ActPublic Sector Pension Investment Board Act
PrecisAppointment of DAVID C. COURT of Toronto, Ontario, to be a director of the Public Sector Pension Investment Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of four years, effective October 30, 2018, in the place of Diane Bean, whose term will expire.
